<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.8.9">
<l>kaṇṇa ṉeṉṟum vāṉa varkaḷ kāta littu malarkaḷ tūvum</l>
<l>eṇṇa ṉeṉṟu miṉpa ṉeṉṟu mēḻu lukuk kāti yeṉṟum</l>
<l>tiṇṇa māṭa nīṭu nāṅkait tēva tēva ṉeṉṟeṉ ṟōti</l>
<l>paṇṇi ṉaṉṉa meṉmo ḻiyāḷ pārttaṉ paḷḷi pāṭu vāḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Saying, “Kaṇṇaṉ,” saying, “The one in the thoughts of celestials</l>
<l rend="indent">[for whom they] lovingly scatter blossoms,”</l>
<l>Saying, “He who is [my] delight,” saying, “Primal cause of the seven worlds,”</l>
<l>Reciting over and over, “God of gods in spacious Nāṅkai</l>
<l rend="indent">with sturdy mansions,”</l>
<l>She, whose soft speech is like a melody, sings of Pārttaṉpaḷḷi.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
